 my hon. Friend’s new clause and hope Committee members consider it kindly. Ordered, That the debate be now adjourned. — (Glyn Davies.)     Share           4.02 pm          Adjourned till Wednesday 14 November at Two o’clock.                     ×   Suggest Correction            Your Details:         Enter your suggested correction:   0 /1000          Please prove you are not a robot.        Close  Submit               A-Z index | Glossary | Contact us | Freedom of Information | Data Protection |  Jobs | Using this website |  Copyright     © Parliamentary Copyright                     Cookies: We use cookies to give you the best possible experience on our site. By continuing to use the site you
